Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,【OP】
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.49,0:00:12.86,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}心神不定  因为我由于不决
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.86,0:00:16.62,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}轻微的颤抖着  control过了还在颤抖
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.62,0:00:20.38,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}太阳也好  运气（月亮）也罢  完全与我无缘
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.38,0:00:21.79,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}“只有硬上了吧”
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.79,0:00:24.48,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我这样劝说自己
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.12,0:00:30.05,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,0)\blur4}情况很糟糕  临阵逃脱又没毅力
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.13,0:00:34.06,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,0)\blur4}虽然前途未卜  也只能靠胆量获胜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.06,0:00:37.55,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}压制着冲动  寻找敌我之间的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.75,0:00:40.84,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,0)\blur4}唯一需要的是胜利的自尊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.84,0:00:43.95,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}能尝下胜利的美酒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.95,0:00:47.94,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}或者喝下满腔的苦水
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.94,0:00:51.70,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}是的  一切都是二择其一
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.70,0:00:55.40,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur4}好想操纵命运的轮盘
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.81,0:01:00.76,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}绝好的黄金时间  亲自把握机会
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.76,0:01:04.84,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}摆出一副扑克脸  设下陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.84,0:01:09.79,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur4}把敌人引入幻想的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.17,0:01:16.14,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}无尽的pressure game  跨越过去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.14,0:01:20.15,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}为了跨越荣耀的borderline
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.15,0:01:24.87,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}How many？  我需要支付多少代价？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.87,0:01:29.09,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur4}到底舍不得放弃哪个？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.01,0:00:00.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,【ED】
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.40,0:21:53.79,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,250)\blur2}一轮又一轮后依然想在此相见
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.86,0:22:00.68,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,500)\blur2}为了不再走散而紧紧牵着手
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.81,0:22:03.33,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\i1}谈话直到日出
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.33,0:22:06.19,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\i1}牵手直到日落
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.19,0:22:11.44,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,250)\blur2\i1}就这样明天后天也一直这样形影不离
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.50,0:22:15.99,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,0)\blur2}寂寞的看着街上
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.99,0:22:21.31,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}一个人是无法找到温暖的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.31,0:22:26.83,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,250)\blur2}第一次知道爱原来可以如此坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.98,0:22:32.66,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,0)\blur2}那是在与你相遇之后
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.66,0:22:37.92,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}一轮又一轮后依然想在此相见
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.92,0:22:43.21,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}为了不再走散而紧紧牵着手
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.21,0:22:48.43,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}因为一个人无法入睡  也无法做梦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.43,0:22:54.20,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}在不安无法到达的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.20,0:22:59.43,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur2}即使是没有星星的夜晚也要继续将其照亮
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.70,0:23:01.93,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\i1}和你在一起的话能到任何地方
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.93,0:23:04.96,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\i1}一个人无法走过的道路  如果是两个人的话
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.96,0:23:08.00,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\i1}就可以哼着歌走过
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.00,0:23:11.39,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur2\i1}只要有你在就很幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.89,0:04:15.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,950)\fn方正大标宋_GBK\fs135\fsp12\blur6\bord5\1c&H00&\3c&HFFFFFFFF&}布里克斯的北壁
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.55,0:01:33.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了调查炼丹术的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.28,0:01:37.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,寻找清国的少女小梅的爱德和阿尔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.46,0:01:41.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得到了她去了北方的情报
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.16,0:01:43.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,另一方面
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.26,0:01:47.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,红莲之炼金术师金普利追逐着
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.18,0:01:51.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从中央都市向西方前进的斯卡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.68,0:01:55.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 斯卡混入夜色中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.70,0:01:58.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.96,0:02:04.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果要从列车上跳车
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.76,0:02:06.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么弯道较多的这里最理想了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.23,0:02:09.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为蒸汽机车会减速
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.68,0:02:14.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,问题是逃向哪边了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.73,0:02:17.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,斯卡的目击情报呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.00,0:02:19.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全没有
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.20,0:02:21.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.73,0:02:24.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到这里之前一直都很显眼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.92,0:02:26.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,报告
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.37,0:02:29.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在南边200米左右的河边
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.45,0:02:31.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有一艘小船被偷了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.73,0:02:32.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是斯卡吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.91,0:02:34.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到现在为止还没有目击情报
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.30,0:02:35.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去调查
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.33,0:02:36.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.47,0:02:38.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,报告
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.00,0:02:43.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住在附近的老人看到奇怪的二人组去了西边
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.12,0:02:44.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这回是西边吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.49,0:02:46.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马上派兵
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.63,0:02:47.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抓住那二个人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.05,0:02:48.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.89,0:02:51.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.19,0:02:53.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 只是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.27,0:02:57.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这地图上有一条向北方前进的山道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.58,0:03:00.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.88,0:03:02.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来是去北方地区的林道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.08,0:03:04.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为落石不断
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.65,0:03:06.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在禁止通行了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.63,0:03:08.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.68,0:03:28.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这前面几处和这里一样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.12,0:03:31.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有巨大的落石把道路封住了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.47,0:03:44.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,水的流向改变了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.26,0:03:46.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.80,0:03:47.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.54,0:03:54.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对于善于破坏的炼金术师
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.55,0:03:58.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要破坏这种程度的障碍物非常容易
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.30,0:03:58.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.01,0:04:01.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同样的 破坏山体
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.46,0:04:05.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用落石把路封住也非常容易
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.45,0:04:08.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,炼成的痕迹？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.75,0:04:11.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把兵派往北方
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.54,0:04:28.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是雪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.57,0:04:43.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.25,0:04:50.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 哥哥居然激动成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.69,0:04:52.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.09,0:04:53.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只不过滑了一跤
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.85,0:04:57.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 真是好大的雪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.75,0:05:02.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 在利塞布尔很少能看到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.56,0:05:04.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 阿尔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.92,0:05:07.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还记得我们小时候在利塞布林见到的大雪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.48,0:05:09.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大雪？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.95,0:05:14.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,记得 记得
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.93,0:05:16.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家打雪仗呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.75,0:05:19.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也做了雪人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.47,0:05:20.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.92,0:05:28.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小时候完全没有想过自己会到北边来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.04,0:05:32.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 还是来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.36,0:05:43.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.20,0:05:47.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,距开往布里克斯的列车发车 还有一点时间
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.90,0:05:49.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去吃点好吃的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.33,0:05:52.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然肚子没饿
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.72,0:05:54.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之去看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.95,0:05:57.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跑步的话又得摔跤了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.03,0:05:58.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.04,0:06:04.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs60}（各地区…）
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.67,0:06:05.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs60}（斯卡的手画像呢）
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.91,0:06:06.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs60}（文件号码…）
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.88,0:06:08.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么情报吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.57,0:06:11.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还在全力搜查 非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.81,0:06:17.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有目击者称 在前一站的列车调度室中看到像斯卡的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.00,0:06:18.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有错吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.44,0:06:20.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.90,0:06:24.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目击情报显示斯卡窜进了去布里克斯的军用列车
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.35,0:06:26.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同行者呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.97,0:06:28.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中年男性 头发是黑的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.07,0:06:29.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和报告书一样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.52,0:06:32.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马上让列车停下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.67,0:06:35.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有那个必要
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.38,0:06:38.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又让他跳车的话就头痛了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.12,0:06:48.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 接下来就是我的工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.17,0:06:51.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们不要妨碍我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.17,0:07:03.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,睡一会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.93,0:07:07.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在北方的寒冷中 想睡也会睡不着
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.19,0:08:01.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要跳过去 请配合好速度
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.19,0:08:02.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.77,0:08:28.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马可医生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.73,0:08:33.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来接你了 你已经逃不掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.59,0:08:35.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一个人嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.00,0:08:37.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,斯卡到哪里去了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.98,0:08:40.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是不死心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.06,0:08:42.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说了你逃不掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.18,0:08:44.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马可医生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.32,0:08:49.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.72,0:09:02.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就是传闻中的伊修瓦尔人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.46,0:09:36.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么能和那些怪物待在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.71,0:09:38.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要跳车的话 就趁现在
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.32,0:09:43.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.03,0:09:57.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐鲁夫·J·金普利
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.22,0:10:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,红莲之炼金术师
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.85,0:10:02.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还记得我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.95,0:10:05.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我记得很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.22,0:10:09.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你曾在伊修瓦尔的干达地区
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.57,0:10:13.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个时候在你身边的是家人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.38,0:10:19.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,记得有个和你一模一样的戴着眼镜的人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.69,0:10:22.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从左侧腹流出大量的血
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.19,0:10:25.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常痛苦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.29,0:10:38.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不太妙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.71,0:10:41.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我刚出狱 身体还很僵硬
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.08,0:10:44.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那边是因为内乱结束后还一直持续战斗至今
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.76,0:10:48.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从体力上说 是我不利
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.55,0:10:51.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 毕竟只会破坏…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.85,0:11:02.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,左侧腹吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.37,0:11:06.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会给你留下向神祈祷的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.73,0:11:10.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真遗憾
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.10,0:11:15.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到两次都杀不死同一个伊修瓦尔人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.65,0:11:34.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然让我逃走 这是极大的屈辱
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.20,0:11:39.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次一定分出胜负 伊修瓦尔人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.55,0:11:51.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,金普利
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.35,0:11:55.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 看不到
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.11,0:11:57.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才的声音是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.85,0:12:08.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,后面的车厢没有了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.44,0:12:11.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.81,0:12:13.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,军队的命令是不准停车
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.33,0:12:15.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.06,0:12:17.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果发生了脱轨事故
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.52,0:12:19.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会成为我们的责任
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.37,0:12:38.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你 发生了什么事？喂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.52,0:12:42.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁说能停下的？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.41,0:12:46.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这么继续前进
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.61,0:12:47.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,向北方前进
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.32,0:12:51.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真不错
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.77,0:12:54.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 死就在眼前
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.14,0:12:57.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,构筑死的人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.38,0:12:59.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被死追逐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.37,0:13:02.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,永远和死相伴
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.97,0:13:08.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赌上灵魂的工作才美丽
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.14,0:13:11.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多么让人有干劲的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.51,0:13:14.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的战场
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.58,0:13:25.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,斯卡先生和尤基先生不要紧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.10,0:13:28.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有追兵来追我们 也就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.02,0:13:32.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们吸引了宪兵的注意力
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.78,0:13:33.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望他们没事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.81,0:13:36.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马可先生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.46,0:13:38.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.11,0:13:40.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对于还没有完全恢复的皮肤来说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.74,0:13:42.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,北方的风有点太厉害了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.41,0:13:44.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.61,0:13:48.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果能治疗成更好看一点的脸就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.53,0:13:52.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 对我来说 这脸才符合我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.95,0:13:54.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经很满足了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.93,0:13:57.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小梅 快看
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.48,0:14:02.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是布里克斯山脉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.77,0:14:06.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作为和北方的大国德拉古马国之间的边境山脉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.69,0:14:11.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该离斯卡指定的地方不远了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.87,0:14:12.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.62,0:14:16.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马上就到了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.70,0:14:42.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,酒店已经退房了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.05,0:14:44.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 就在昨天
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.01,0:14:46.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道去哪里了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.19,0:14:49.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,记得说是要去北方
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.05,0:14:52.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗 受您照顾了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.62,0:14:56.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.57,0:14:58.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.98,0:15:00.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那对兄弟还精神吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.35,0:15:03.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就那么去了北方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.63,0:15:06.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.17,0:15:08.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会死呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.57,0:15:14.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥 感冒了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.48,0:15:16.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.67,0:15:18.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是布里克斯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.79,0:15:21.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这里了 两位小哥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.04,0:15:27.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直沿着这条山道走的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.39,0:15:28.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就会到达布里克斯要塞
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.01,0:15:29.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.35,0:15:31.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.61,0:15:34.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对 就是你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.99,0:15:36.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是机械铠吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.72,0:15:37.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.89,0:15:40.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗 那就没问题了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.78,0:15:43.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.56,0:15:44.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.20,0:15:49.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,栅栏那边是军队的所有地
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.31,0:15:51.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果没沿着路走会死的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.91,0:15:52.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.99,0:15:55.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.14,0:15:56.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.64,0:16:14.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽说山里的天气变得快
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.63,0:16:16.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到变得有那么快
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.86,0:16:18.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.51,0:16:20.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全找不到路了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.85,0:16:21.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.27,0:16:23.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊兹米师傅在修行时代
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.96,0:16:26.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被放置在冬天的布里克斯山一个月
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.78,0:16:27.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也生还了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.19,0:16:29.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,骗人的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.50,0:16:32.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这里哪活得了一个月
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.56,0:16:34.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 据说还打倒了熊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.91,0:16:38.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布里克斯的熊如果站起来能超过两米
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.83,0:16:40.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能打倒它
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.53,0:16:48.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,熊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.42,0:16:58.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是熊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.90,0:17:02.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿尔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.23,0:17:06.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.88,0:17:08.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那不是国军的军服吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.86,0:17:11.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你小子也是机械铠吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.06,0:17:13.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是个平凡的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.90,0:17:17.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？倒是你装了个没品位的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.74,0:17:21.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道这机械美 真是愚蠢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.93,0:17:26.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,战斗用机械铠 M1913-A鳄鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.41,0:17:30.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不想被咬碎的话就乖乖束手就擒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.78,0:17:32.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这德拉古马密探
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.97,0:17:33.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,密探？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.20,0:17:35.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在说什么 我是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.76,0:17:37.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.47,0:17:42.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说不通的大家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.01,0:17:45.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个疼痛是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.57,0:17:48.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,机械铠没法正常活动
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.39,0:17:51.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,取下了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.94,0:17:53.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.04,0:17:55.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.24,0:17:57.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我好好听人说话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.51,0:17:59.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还要反抗吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.58,0:18:04.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.19,0:18:07.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 等等 等等…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.43,0:18:10.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这下等机械铠我取走了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.84,0:18:15.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要拿走的是你的手臂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.38,0:18:19.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你做了什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.64,0:18:23.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等等等等等 暂停
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.68,0:18:25.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么炼金术不起作用
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.03,0:18:27.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是铁吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.99,0:18:28.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.49,0:18:32.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢 阿尔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.76,0:18:38.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要紧吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.45,0:18:39.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.83,0:18:42.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在冻死在雪山之前会先被温莉杀了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.56,0:18:44.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不错嘛 小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.24,0:18:47.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用普通的机械铠已经很不错了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.34,0:18:49.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 到此为止了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.73,0:19:01.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布里克斯的山岳警备兵
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.32,0:19:05.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂 又被枪指着了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.68,0:19:12.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.18,0:19:13.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,墙壁？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.55,0:19:16.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 帕卡尼亚大尉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.18,0:19:17.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.01,0:19:19.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在此喧闹 非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.09,0:19:21.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿姆斯壮少将阁下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.97,0:19:30.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿姆斯壮是？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.01,0:19:34.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是阿姆斯壮少佐说要介绍的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.77,0:19:37.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奥莉薇·米拉·阿姆斯壮
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.02,0:19:40.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿姆斯壮少佐的姐姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.43,0:19:43.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.86,0:19:47.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不像
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.43,0:19:49.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不大
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.35,0:19:51.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.63,0:19:55.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是钢之炼金术师 爱德华·艾尔利克
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.51,0:19:58.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,经中央都市的阿姆斯壮少佐的介绍
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.37,0:20:01.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来见少将阁下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.23,0:20:04.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望能让警备兵让开
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.71,0:20:06.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搜身
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.12,0:20:07.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.14,0:20:09.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是可疑人物
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.91,0:20:10.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.52,0:20:14.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁都可以自称是名人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.13,0:20:17.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 空的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.50,0:20:18.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.44,0:20:20.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.95,0:20:22.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阁下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.60,0:20:26.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是亚力士·路易·阿姆斯壮少佐的介绍信
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.67,0:20:30.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要读了 就知道我们不是可疑人物
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.05,0:20:35.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确实是亚力士的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.63,0:20:40.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什…什么 你不读吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.97,0:20:43.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对我来说介绍信什么的没有意义
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.19,0:20:47.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不需要别人给的评价
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.06,0:20:50.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会用我的眼睛来判断一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.39,0:21:07.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真…真厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.45,0:21:09.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好大
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.21,0:21:11.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.96,0:21:14.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,进来 钢之炼金术师
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.32,0:21:18.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,厉害 好高 好大
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.18,0:21:21.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还不快走 垃圾们
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.08,0:21:24.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再不走当心我拔掉你头上的天线
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.53,0:21:31.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说在前头 不会把你当小孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.86,0:21:34.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是天险之地
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.69,0:21:35.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布里克斯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.66,0:21:38.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弱肉强食的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.78,0:23:20.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.17,0:23:32.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是斯卡哥哥的研究书
